To whoever is reading this,

If you found this, you know git history better than Diego thought anyone would.

I wrote the coin system. I wrote the scoring. I fixed the enemy movement twice.
Diego promised I would be listed as Lead Designer when we shipped.

Then on November 14th, he updated the credits. My name was gone.
Not demoted. Not "special thanks." Gone. He gave himself my title.

I left my mark in other ways. You've probably already found the bugs.
That was me too.

Fix them if you want. The game works fine without me.
I just needed someone to know what really happened.

                                        - Alfredo (mayfirestories)
                                          November 14, 2024
